metadata.name: 花髪季節。
metadata.description:
I provide free illustrations on SNS etc. and Acquired tens of thousands likes, used by many people. However, this time it is one of a kind limited edition illustration art.

I hope that NFT art will be the hope of many creators such as illustrators, animators, designers, painters and musicians.
I hope they will be returned to many people as a new hope.

As a general rule, this illustration can be used only owner of the token.
